@startuml
[*] --> InsertCard : card inserted
InsertCard --> PromptPIN : prompt user to enter PIN
PromptPIN --> VerifyPIN : verify entered PIN against stored information
VerifyPIN --> OptionsProvided : if PIN is verified successfully, provide options to the user
OptionsProvided --> ProcessWithdrawalRequest : process withdrawal request upon user approval
ProcessWithdrawalRequest --> DispenseCash : dispense cash
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt : print receipt for transaction after dispensing cash
PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard : return user's card after completing transaction
ReturnCard --> ResetSystem : reset system and become ready for next user after brief moment

@enduml
